# This Vercel deploy targets the PUBLIC static tour + demo (/tour, /demo),
# which need no backend and no audio. The ~215MB of pre-generated practice
# audio is only used by the authenticated app (which redirects to /auth on a
# static deploy), so we exclude it to keep deploys small and fast.
#
# The prebuild audio-consistency check only reads data/audio_index.json, so
# excluding these directories does not affect the build.
audio/
public/audio/
